menu.name: House Coffee
menu.description: Authentic Vietnamese Style Creamy Iced CoffeePerfected over the time span of a hundred years, Cafe Sua Da has become one of the world’s most refined and popular drinks. menu.name: Vietnamese Coffee
menu.description: Traditional Vietnamese Iced CoffeeStrong coffee with sweetened condensed milk and chilled on ice makes an unbeatable Southeast Asian treat. menu.name: Mung Bean Milk Tea
menu.description: Jasmine Tea with Mung Bean and Pandan LeavesThat Mung bean flavor you are tasting? Yes, it’s real Mung bean. Cooked, strained, and blended Mung bean has a slightly sweet and unique earthy tone that is perfect for Milk Tea infusion. But the Mung bean is not the only thing that is real. menu.name: Jasmine Milk Tea

menu.name: Sea Cream Jasmine Tea
menu.description: Jasmine Green Tea Topped with Our Signature Whipped Sea CreamOur award-winning jasmine blended with jasmine petals is grown in the high mountains and harvested every spring in the early morning before they bloom to preserve their naturally subtle sweetness. menu.name: Green Thai Tea

menu.name: Japanese Matcha Tea
menu.description: The Healthiest Drink Nature Has to OfferMatcha is known today as the healthiest, rarest and most premium of all tea varieties from Japan. For over 800 years, Zen Buddhist monks have been using Matcha green for meditation purposes. It is extremely exquisite with only a few dozen farmers having the required knowledge to produce it, and we are proud to source our Matcha from such master tea farmers. There is no other fruit or vegetable in the world that provides more antioxidants than Matcha. It is literally the healthiest drink nature has to offer.Calories: 125 - 160

menu.name: Herbal Tea

address: Gyu-Kaku Japanese BBQ, 510 Gray St, Houston, TX 77002, USA

menu.name: Gyu-Bento: Build Your Own Bento!
menu.description: The closest you can get to the Gyu-Kaku yakiniku experience without grilling the meat yourself. Customize your meal! Select two proteins, two marinades, two sides, and rice portion. Includes Miso Soup, White Rice, and Half Gyu-Kaku Salad.

menu.name: Umakara Beef Bowl
menu.description: Thin-sliced Yakishabu beef marinated in our sweet & spicy Umakara sauce with sliced onions on a bed of white rice and shredded cabbage. Topped with chopped green onions and sesame seeds.

menu.name: Sukiyaki Fried Rice with Beef Bowl
menu.description: Our signature thin-sliced Sukiyaki-marinated beef stir-fried with white rice, egg yolk, mushrooms, and sliced onions. Topped with diced red bell peppers, chopped green onions, and sesame seeds.

menu.name: Fried Chicken Karaage Bowl
menu.description: Japanese Fried Chicken Karaage on a bed of white rice and shredded cabbage. Topped with Japanese Chili Mayo and chopped green onions.

menu.name: Garlic Fried Rice Bowl
menu.description: Our Garlic Fried Rice features white rice stir-fried with egg yolk, sliced onions, sliced garlic. Seasoned with a combination of our Shio Soy Sauce, butter, sesame oil, and black pepper. Topped with chopped green onions and fried garlic chips.

menu.name: Beyond Bibimbap Bowl
menu.description: Our beloved Sukiyaki Bibimbap goes BEYOND. 100% plant-based Beyond Beef is marinated in our secret Sukiyaki sauce and stir fried with mushrooms, diced red bell peppers, and sliced white onions. Served over rice. Topped with chopped green onions and sesame seeds. Also contains butter and sesame oil. Picture for visualization purposes only. Beyond Bibimbap will arrive pre-mixed.

menu.name: Garlic Noodles with Chicken
menu.description: Thick Japanese noodles stir-fried with chicken, sliced garlic, butter, and soy sauce. Topped with diced red bell peppers, chopped green onions, and sesame seeds.

menu.name: Spicy Beef Ramen
menu.description: Gyu-Kaku original recipe: Japanese BBQ meets Ramen! Rich kalbi beef soup and medium thickness ramen noodles topped with thin-sliced beef, boiled egg, green onions, spinach, daikon radish, and sesame seeds. Ramen noodles and hot soup are packaged separately to maintain their maximum deliciousness. Please reheat soup in the microwave (if necessary) and pour over noodles.

menu.name: Garlic Noodles with Crunchy Garlic Shrimp
menu.description: Crunchy Garlic Shrimp atop thick Japanese noodles stir-fried with sliced garlic, butter, and soy sauce. Topped with diced red bell peppers, chopped green onions, and sesame seeds.

menu.name: Tonkotsu Kakuni Ramen
menu.description: Our Tonkotsu pork bone ramen comes with chunky, fatty braised pork belly Kakuni chashu and is topped with hard-boiled egg, chopped green onions, diced red bell peppers, and sesame seeds. Ramen noodles and hot soup are packaged separately to maintain their maximum deliciousness. Please reheat soup in the microwave (if necessary) and pour over noodles.

menu.name: Miso Yaki-Udon
menu.description: Thick, chewy udon noodles stir-fried with pork belly in our special miso-based sauce. Includes sliced mushrooms, onions, broccoli, shredded cabbage, chopped red bell peppers, and green onions. Finished with bonito flakes and a dash of sesame seeds.

menu.name: Goma Negi Shio Ramen
menu.description: Beef and shio-based soup with medium-thick ramen noodles and thick braised pork belly Kakuni chashu. Toppings also include boiled egg, green onion, and sesame seeds. Ramen noodles and hot soup are packaged separately to maintain their maximum deliciousness. Please reheat soup in the microwave (if necessary) and pour over noodles.

menu.name: MEGA Garlic Noodles with Chicken
menu.description: A TRIPLE SERVING of our Crowd Favorite: Mega Garlic Noodles with Chicken. Serves 3-5 people. Thick Japanese noodles stir-fried with chicken, sliced garlic, butter, and soy sauce. Topped with diced red bell peppers, chopped green onions, and sesame seeds.

menu.name: Mega Sukiyaki Fried Rice with Beef
menu.description: A TRIPLE SERVING of our Crowd Favorite: Sukiyaki Fried Rice with Beef. Serves 3-5 people. Our signature thin-sliced Sukiyaki-marinated beef stir-fried with white rice, egg yolk, mushrooms, and sliced onions. Topped with diced red bell peppers, chopped green Onions, and sesame seeds.

menu.name: Half Gyu-Kaku Salad
menu.description: Mixed greens, sliced cucumber, cherry tomatoes, and diced red bell pepper. Topped with a boiled egg (sliced), shredded daikon radish, and shredded cabbage. Served with Gyu-Kaku Dressing on the side.

menu.name: Single S'more
menu.description: A single S'more pre-softened, wrapped-up, and ready to eat! Graham Cracker, marshmallow, and milk chocolate.

menu.name: Gyu-Combo: 2 Choice of Protein

Ramen noodles and hot soup are packaged separately to maintain their maximum deliciousness. Please reheat soup in the microwave (if necessary) and pour over noodles.

menu.name: Chardonnay, Rombauer
menu.description: Ripe peach, citrus fruits, spice, and pie crust aromas all mingle and lift from the glass. The citrus supported by notes of apricot continues onto the palate which is concentrated with a rich, creamy middle palate, and strong supporting acidity. The finish is long and marked with hints of vanilla. This wine will continue to build richness as it ages in the bottle.

menu.name: Rosé, Beaujolais Rosé, Kermit Lynch
menu.description: A simple Beaujolais in name and in price, Dupeuble’s rosé (and red . . . and white, for that matter) should not be mistaken for a basic bottle of wine. Sure, it is supremely thirst-quenching, as any self-respecting rosé should be, and it is darn fun to drink—we are talking about Beaujolais, after all. But consider that the Gamay vines here are up to seventy years old, and they grow in an intricate mix of granite, clay, and sandy soils. The outcome is a wine of real substance, with an extra dimension of depth along with an array of delightful flavors and textures.

menu.name: Sparkling, Azimut Brut Cava Nature
menu.description: This organic sparkling wine hails from the Catalonia region of Spain. Fresh citrus and stone fruit aromas layered with hints of bergamot and chamomile. On the palate, more citrus and white flowers, but with nutty notes. Despite the natural style, and minimal intervention, these are some clean, refreshing, and crushable bubbles.

menu.name: Orange Wine, Skins by Field Recordings
menu.description: This Paso Robles skin-contact orange wine is a very approachable blend made of Chenin Blanc, Verdelho, and Pinot Gris. Dry with flavors of apricot, vanilla & citrus  that pair well with spicy foods and pork or salmon.

menu.name: Malbec, Red Schooner
menu.description: Dry, medium to full bodied Malbec produced by the highly acclaimed Wagner family of Caymus. Silky and smooth on the palate, with more lush plum and ripe tannins carrying through to a long finish. BEST VALUE WINE for this price point!

menu.name: Cabernet, Lucky Draw by 689
menu.description: Soon-to-be your new house staple! From Napa, Lucky Draw combines the deep intense flavors of Cabernet Sauvignon with a touch of Malbec to add additional depth and complexity. Deep purple in color, the wine highlights delicious flavors of blueberry, dark cherry and cocoa. Full-bodied with depth and structure, the wine finishes with silky tannins. It’s a sophisticated wine without all the pretension.

menu.name: Red Blend, Cain Cuvée NV17
menu.description: This multi vintage Cabernet blend is not your typical Napa red wine; no big, inky, oaky blockbuster here. Made in Bordeaux style with layers of complexity for serious wine-lovers who value balance and finish. Notes of raspberries, red cherries, forest, and earth throughout the palate. The Cuvée NV17 is for those who know that wine doesn't have to be big to be good. Biodynamic

menu.description: As delicious as our sandwiches are, they are even better when paired with the perfect side and drink or even adding a little something extra. With such a variety to choose from, there's truly something for every taste.

menu.name: #4 Supreme Meats
menu.description: One sandwich reigns supreme. Black Forest ham, Genoa salami, pepperoni, and our capicola on fresh-baked Artisan Italian bread with provolone cheese, lettuce, tomatoes, red onions, and banana peppers…all topped off with our famous MVP Parmesan Vinaigrette®.

menu.name: #11 Subway Club®
menu.description: Oven-roasted turkey, Black Forest ham, USDA Choice Roast Beef, provolone cheese piled on Hearty Multigrain bread and topped with lettuce, tomatoes, red onions, and mayo. A club sandwich the Subway® style.

menu.name: #6 The Boss
menu.description: It’s the mother of all meatball subs. Juicy meatballs drenched in marinara sauce with slices of pepperoni and BelGioioso® Fresh Mozzarella. Sprinkled with parmesan and served toasted on Italian Herbs & Cheese bread.

menu.name: #12 Turkey Cali Club™
menu.description: Eat fresh, California style. Oven-roasted turkey, crisp bacon, BelGioioso® Fresh Mozzarella, and smashed Hass avocado. Topped with spinach, tomatoes, red onions, and mayo toasted on Hearty Multigrain bread.

menu.name: #9 The Champ™
menu.description: Tender hand-pulled rotisserie-style chicken, a double helping of Monterey Cheddar, green peppers, and red onions. Topped off with creamy Peppercorn Ranch and served toasted on Artisan Italian bread. This one’s a winner!

menu.name: #3 The Monster™
menu.description: Got a monstrous appetite? We’re talking thick juicy steak, crisp bacon, a double helping of Monterey cheddar, green peppers and red onions piled high and served toasted on Artisan Italian bread and topped off with creamy Peppercorn Ranch.

menu.name: #10 All-American Club®
menu.description: The American classic. Oven-roasted turkey, Black Forest ham, crisp bacon, and American cheese with lettuce, tomatoes, red onions, and mayo. Served toasted on Artisan Italian bread.

menu.name: #8 The Great Garlic™
menu.description: Our NEW creamy garlic sauce is the secret to this sub. We pile juicy rotisserie-style chicken, crispy bacon, provolone, lettuce, tomatoes, red onions served toasted on Artisan Italian bread…all topped off with our NEW creamy Roasted Garlic Aioli. Irresistible!

menu.name: #1 The Philly
menu.description: The classic cheesesteak stacked with juicy steak and a double helping of provolone toasted on Artisan Italian bread and topped with green peppers, red onions and mayo.

menu.name: #7 The MexiCali
menu.description: Head for the Southwest with juicy rotisserie-style chicken, smashed avocado, double Pepper Jack cheese, lettuce, tomatoes, and red onions topped with our smoky Baja Chipotle sauce and served toasted on Artisan Italian bread.

menu.name: #5 Bella Mozza
menu.description: Lotsa meat and lotsa mozzarella make this special. Thin-sliced Black Forest ham, our capicola, and BelGioioso® Fresh Mozzarella on fresh-baked Artisan Italian bread. Topped with spinach, tomatoes, red onions, and banana peppers and drizzled with our tangy MVP Parmesan Vinaigrette®.

menu.name: #2 The Outlaw™
menu.description: Spicy, cheesy, smoky — this one’s got it all. Juicy steak meets double Pepper Jack cheese, with green peppers, red onions, and Baja Chipotle sauce toasted on Artisan Italian bread. Try not to fall head over heels.

menu.name: Oven Roasted Turkey
menu.description: If a classic is what you crave, our thin-sliced Oven Roasted Turkey is the sandwich for you. It’s full of flavor and made to order with your choice of crisp veggies, served on our freshly baked, Hearty Multigrain bread.

menu.name: Tuna
menu.description: You’ll love every bite of our classic tuna sandwich. 100% wild caught tuna blended with creamy mayo then topped with your choice of crisp, fresh veggies. 100% delicious.

menu.name: Meatball Marinara
menu.description: The Meatball Marinara sandwich is drenched in irresistible marinara sauce, sprinkled with Parmesan cheese,  topped with whatever you want (no judgement) and perfectly toasted just for you.

menu.name: Steak & Cheese
menu.description: Our Steak & Cheese sandwich is where warm, delicious steak gets topped with melty cheesiness. Get crazy with veggies and sauces to make it what you want.

menu.name: Black Forest Ham
menu.description: Our Black Forest Ham sandwich is a true classic. We add lettuce, baby spinach, cucumbers, green peppers and red onions to our delicious, thin-sliced ham and serve it on our Hearty Multigrain bread. Want cheese? Just ask.

menu.name: Sweet Onion Chicken Teriyaki
menu.description: The Sweet Onion Chicken Teriyaki sub is one sah-weeet sub. It starts with Hearty Multigrain bread, add perfectly cooked grilled chicken strips, marinated in our NEW Sweet Onion Teriyaki Sauce, then pile on the crunch with lettuce, spinach, tomatoes, cucumbers, green peppers, red onions and top with another pass of our NEW Sweet Onion Teriyaki sauce.

menu.name: Italian B.M.T.®
menu.description: The Italian B.M.T.® sandwich is filled with Genoa salami, spicy pepperoni, and Black Forest Ham. Big. Meaty. Tasty. Get it.

menu.name: Spicy Italian
menu.description: Our Spicy Italian sandwich is a combo of pepperoni and Genoa salami. Pile on cheese, crunchy veggies, and finish it with your favorite sauce. Or don't. Your call.

menu.name: Veggie Delite®
menu.description: The Veggie Delite® sandwich is crispy, crunchy, vegetarian perfection. With lettuce, baby spinach, tomatoes, cucumbers, green peppers and red onions, all on our Hearty Multigrain bread.

menu.name: Cold Cut Combo®
menu.description: The Cold Cut Combo® sandwich with ham, salami, and bologna (all turkey based) is a long-time Subway® favorite. Yeah. It's that good.

menu.name: Chicken & Bacon Ranch
menu.description: What do you get when you mix juicy Rotisserie-Style Chicken, melty Monterey Cheddar Cheese, Hickory-Smoked Bacon, and our creamy Peppercorn Ranch? Your sandwich happy place.

Our Buffalo Chicken Footlong is made with everyone’s favorite hot sauce – Frank’s RedHot® and topped with peppercorn ranch. Try it with lettuce, tomatoes and cucumbers! menu.description: It starts with rich cocoa cookie dough sprinkled end to end with semi-sweet chocolate chips and sweet white chips, baked fresh to be crispy outside, soft inside.  Try our most chocolatey cookie ever and be doubly happy.

menu.name: Lay's® Dill Pickle (230 Cals)
menu.description: It all starts with farm-grown potatoes, cooked and seasoned to perfection. Then we add the flavor of dill pickle. So every LAY'S® potato chip is perfectly crispy and delicious.

menu.name: 6 Pack Cookie Box (0 Cals)
menu.description: Our New 6 Pack Cookie Box is the most delicious out-of-the-box thinking. That’s because you can get 1 of our 5 delectable fresh-baked cookies in one place. One for you, one for him, one for her and even more to keep sharing…or not! Get the New 6 Pack Cookie Box today and get that sweet treat you’re craving.

menu.name: 12 Pack Cookie Box (0 Cals)
menu.description: 12 cookies. 1 delicious order. That’s what our new 12 Cookie Box is all about. You get a dozen of 1 of our 5 delectable fresh-baked cookies and a one-way ticket to sweet treats that you can share with friends, family or co-workers. With so many choices, there’s a cookie for everyone.

menu.name: #6 The Boss
menu.description: It’s the mother of all meatball subs. Juicy meatballs drenched in marinara sauce with slices of pepperoni and BelGioioso® Fresh Mozzarella. Sprinkled with parmesan and served toasted on Italian Herbs & Cheese bread.

menu.name: #2 The Outlaw™
menu.description: Spicy, cheesy, smoky — this one’s got it all. Juicy steak meets double Pepper Jack cheese, with green peppers, red onions, and Baja Chipotle sauce toasted on Artisan Italian bread. Try not to fall head over heels.

menu.name: #9 The Champ™
menu.description: Tender hand-pulled rotisserie-style chicken, a double helping of Monterey Cheddar, green peppers, and red onions. Topped off with creamy Peppercorn Ranch and served toasted on Artisan Italian bread. This one’s a winner!

menu.name: #4 Supreme Meats
menu.description: One sandwich reigns supreme. Black Forest ham, Genoa salami, pepperoni, and our capicola on fresh-baked Artisan Italian bread with provolone cheese, lettuce, tomatoes, red onions, and banana peppers…all topped off with our famous MVP Parmesan Vinaigrette®.

menu.name: #10 All-American Club®
menu.description: The American classic. Oven-roasted turkey, Black Forest ham, crisp bacon, and American cheese with lettuce, tomatoes, red onions, and mayo. Served toasted on Artisan Italian bread.

menu.name: #11 Subway Club®
menu.description: Oven-roasted turkey, Black Forest ham, USDA Choice Roast Beef, provolone cheese piled on Hearty Multigrain bread and topped with lettuce, tomatoes, red onions, and mayo. A club sandwich the Subway® style.

menu.name: #1 The Philly
menu.description: The classic cheesesteak stacked with juicy steak and a double helping of provolone toasted on Artisan Italian bread and topped with green peppers, red onions and mayo.

menu.name: #3 The Monster™
menu.description: Got a monstrous appetite? We’re talking thick juicy steak, crisp bacon, a double helping of Monterey cheddar, green peppers and red onions piled high and served toasted on Artisan Italian bread and topped off with creamy Peppercorn Ranch.

menu.name: #5 Bella Mozza
menu.description: Lotsa meat and lotsa mozzarella make this special. Thin-sliced Black Forest ham, our capicola, and BelGioioso® Fresh Mozzarella on fresh-baked Artisan Italian bread. Topped with spinach, tomatoes, red onions, and banana peppers and drizzled with our tangy MVP Parmesan Vinaigrette®.

menu.name: #7 The MexiCali
menu.description: Head for the Southwest with juicy rotisserie-style chicken, smashed avocado, double Pepper Jack cheese, lettuce, tomatoes, and red onions topped with our smoky Baja Chipotle sauce and served toasted on Artisan Italian bread.

menu.name: #8 The Great Garlic™
menu.description: Our NEW creamy garlic sauce is the secret to this sub. We pile juicy rotisserie-style chicken, crispy bacon, provolone, lettuce, tomatoes, red onions served toasted on Artisan Italian bread…all topped off with our NEW creamy Roasted Garlic Aioli. Irresistible!

menu.name: #12 Turkey Cali Club™
menu.description: Eat fresh, California style. Oven-roasted turkey, crisp bacon, BelGioioso® Fresh Mozzarella, and smashed Hass avocado. Topped with spinach, tomatoes, red onions, and mayo toasted on Hearty Multigrain bread.

menu.name: Tuna
menu.description: You’ll love every bite of our classic tuna sandwich. 100% wild caught tuna blended with creamy mayo then topped with your choice of crisp, fresh veggies. 100% delicious.

menu.name: Oven Roasted Turkey
menu.description: If a classic is what you crave, our thin-sliced Oven Roasted Turkey is the sandwich for you. It’s full of flavor and made to order with your choice of crisp veggies, served on our freshly baked, Hearty Multigrain bread.

menu.name: Black Forest Ham
menu.description: Our Black Forest Ham sandwich is a true classic. We add lettuce, baby spinach, cucumbers, green peppers and red onions to our delicious, thin-sliced ham and serve it on our Hearty Multigrain bread. Want cheese? Just ask.

menu.name: Spicy Italian
menu.description: Our Spicy Italian sandwich is a combo of pepperoni and Genoa salami. Pile on cheese, crunchy veggies, and finish it with your favorite sauce. Or don't. Your call.

menu.name: Cold Cut Combo®
menu.description: The Cold Cut Combo® sandwich with ham, salami, and bologna (all turkey based) is a long-time Subway® favorite. Yeah. It's that good.

menu.name: Italian B.M.T.®
menu.description: The Italian B.M.T.® sandwich is filled with Genoa salami, spicy pepperoni, and Black Forest Ham. Big. Meaty. Tasty. Get it.

menu.name: Meatball Marinara
menu.description: The Meatball Marinara sandwich is drenched in irresistible marinara sauce, sprinkled with Parmesan cheese,  topped with whatever you want (no judgement) and perfectly toasted just for you.

menu.name: Roast Beef
menu.description: Choice Angus Roast Beef, Hearty Multigrain Bread, and plenty of fresh veggies make this lunchtime classic one to remember.

menu.name: Steak & Cheese
menu.description: Our Steak & Cheese sandwich is where warm, delicious steak gets topped with melty cheesiness. Get crazy with veggies and sauces to make it what you want.

menu.name: Veggie Delite®
menu.description: The Veggie Delite® sandwich is crispy, crunchy, vegetarian perfection. With lettuce, baby spinach, tomatoes, cucumbers, green peppers and red onions, all on our Hearty Multigrain bread.

menu.name: Buffalo Chicken
menu.description: When you’re looking to spice things up, do it with Frank’s RedHot® and buffalo chicken. Our Buffalo Chicken Footlong is made with everyone’s favorite hot sauce – Frank’s RedHot® and topped with peppercorn ranch. Try it with lettuce, tomatoes and cucumbers! Frank’s RedHot® is a registered trademark of McCormick & Co. and used under license by Subway Franchisee Advertising Fund Trust Ltd.®/© Subway IP LLC 2021.

menu.name: Chicken & Bacon Ranch
menu.description: What do you get when you mix juicy Rotisserie-Style Chicken, melty Monterey Cheddar Cheese, Hickory-Smoked Bacon, and our creamy Peppercorn Ranch? Your sandwich happy place.

menu.name: Grilled Chicken
menu.description: Tender grilled chicken loaded on our Hearty Multigrain bread with your choice of veggies. A little lettuce, tomatoes, onions and baby spinach, and you can’t go wrong.

menu.name: Rotisserie-Style Chicken
menu.description: Who doesn’t love tender, juicy rotisserie-style chicken? Especially when it’s served on our Hearty Multigrain bread with your choice of veggies. We like lettuce, tomatoes, red onions, and peppers, but hey, it’s your sandwich, do what you like.

menu.name: Oven Roasted Turkey & Ham
menu.description: Enjoy the flavor of tender, thin-sliced oven roasted turkey and Black Forest Ham with your favorite veggies, from juicy tomatoes to sweet red onions, all served on freshly baked, Hearty Multigrain bread.

menu.name: Veggie Patty
menu.description: Delicious vegan patties with lettuce, tomatoes, cucumbers, green peppers and red onions, all served on our freshly baked Hearty Multigrain bread.

menu.name: Chicken & Bacon Ranch Melt
menu.description: How can you improve Rotisserie-Style Chicken, Hickory-Smoked Bacon, and Peppercorn Ranch? With a whole lot of gooey Provolone Cheese and veggies.

menu.name: Meatball Marinara Melt
menu.description: Add some melty goodness to your Meatball Marinara sub. Make it a Fresh Melt™ and get craveable meatballs and tangy marinara sauce topped with American and parmesan, all grilled to cheesy perfection. Freshly made in front of you.

menu.name: Tuna Melt
menu.description: 100% wild-caught tuna with mayo. Fresh onion. Melty provolone. We brought the best ingredients together for something that satisfies your cravings for both fresh and savory. It’s not just a tuna melt, it’s a Fresh Melt™. Freshly made in front of you.

menu.name: Oven Roasted Turkey Melt
menu.description: The Oven Roasted Turkey Melt is loaded with fresh veggies like tomatoes, peppers and onions, and grilled on our Hearty Multigrain bread until the American cheese is as melty and cheesy as you want it. Cravings, covered.

menu.name: Spicy Italian Melt
menu.description: Spicy Italian Melt combines the mouth-watering flavor of pepperoni, salami and cheese grilled to melty perfection with the feel-good flavor of spinach, tomatoes and peppers. Guess you can have it all.

menu.name: Buffalo Chicken Melt
menu.description: Packed with grilled chicken, plus just the right amount of Frank's RedHot® Buffalo sauce, a little peppercorn ranch to beat the heat and all the veggies you can fit in there. Frank’s RedHot® is a registered trademark of McCormick & Co. and used under license by Subway Franchisee Advertising Fund Trust Ltd. ®/© Subway IP LLC 2021.

menu.name: Ham & Cheese Melt
menu.description: Your cravings called, and we answered with melty goodness and fresh veggies, too. The Ham & Cheese Melt combines Black Forest ham, fresh tomato and American cheese and grills them all up to create an indulgent choice that’s freshly made, too.

menu.name: Steak & Cheese Melt
menu.description: Grilled, melty and cheesy but also loaded with fresh vegetables? The Steak & Cheese Melt is just that, freshly made with onions and peppers and perfectly grilled to cover all your cravings.

menu.name: Bacon, Egg & Cheese
menu.description: Start your day in a sizzlin' way with  bacon, egg, and melty cheese on freshly toasted flatbread (or whatever you like). Pile on your favorite veggies and sauce. Start the day right.

menu.name: Steak, Egg & Cheese
menu.description: No matter what side of the bed you wake up on, you’ll love this. Yummy egg  with tender and delicious steak covered in melty cheese. That's one beautiful breakfast.

menu.name: Black Forest Ham, Egg & Cheese
menu.description: Enjoy savory Black Forest ham, melted cheese, and egg -  all on your favorite bread. Add your choice of veggies for a tasty way to start the day. Hello, delicious.

menu.name: Egg & Cheese
menu.description: A classic for a reason. Our Egg and Cheese is simply delicious. Enjoy a fluffy egg with melted cheese. Try it toasted - It's unbeatable.
